                        <interp inst="t18430703-name-348" type="given" value="SETH"></interp>SETH SMITH</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Carey-street—the prisoner was in my employ. I left home on the 20th of April, and left my shop in the prisoner's care—I re<lb></lb>turned on the 8th of June, and missed three pictures, which were safe when I left—on the 9th of June I asked the prisoner about them—he said he had pledged them, and the duplicates were in the drawer, where I found them.</p>
