               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> My master left me with 5<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; I was obliged to pledge them; I told him I would redeem them, or pay so much per week off; I did not intend to steal them; he said he would do so at first, and then he would not.</p>
